data.description: This custom-built two-story home offers all the bells and whistles! Located on 1.34 acres, you will be impressed by the high end upgrades throughout. Specialty made cabinets, upgraded plumbing and lighting fixtures, travertine flooring, arched openings - this house is truly one of a kind! The open concept kitchen has a large gourmet island with plenty of space to entertain guests. The double entry staircase leads to three bedrooms up and a separate entry for your media room or fifth bedroom. You'll also love the added convenience of two half baths. But that's not all - step outside onto your 36x14 patio with outdoor kitchen and take a dip in your in-ground pool/spa oasis! With so much space inside and out, this home is perfect for hosting parties or just enjoying time with family & friends.
